    <text id="A6303T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Sibert reports on family news and his inability to visit this weekend.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-05-26">May 26 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>My Dear Mollie</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>Your dear &amp; welcome letter of the 19th has <orig reg="been">bin</orig>
                    <abbr expan="received">recd</abbr> &amp; read with much pleasure, you Must
                    blame me this for writing you a long letter. I have <orig reg="been">bin</orig>
                    so <orig reg="busy">Bussey</orig> all the Morning that I have not had time to
                    write to you my love. I am so glad that Ada has come so you can spend the Summer
                    with Ella she will <orig reg="move">moove</orig> next week in her new house</p>

                <p>I am sorry I <orig reg="can't">cant</orig> pay you my usual visit this Saturday.
                    Brother is <pb n="2"/>
                    <orig reg="moving">mooveing</orig> &amp; it will be <orig reg="impossible"
                        >imposibe</orig> for me to get off I will be down Saturday a week for <orig
                        reg="certain">Surtien</orig></p>

                <p>I still love you the Same with all my heart &amp; Soul. I must Close Else I
                        <orig reg="won't">wont</orig> get this note in the office in time for the
                    Mail</p>

                <p>My love to your Ma &amp; Pa Excuse this writing it was <orig reg="done"
                    >dun</orig> in haste Ella &amp; family are all well I send love &amp; a
                    Kiss to you my love. I do wish I could come down this Saturday to See you but I
                        <orig reg="can't">cant</orig> God Bless you good bye</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours</salute>
                    <signed>D H Evans</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
